{"tid":2026805,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS中國商店遭整頓「無限期」暫停服務，Xbox One中國版亦緊急「優化」跨區購買未審批遊戲的漏洞","createTime":"2020-05-21T07:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T07:02:23.000Z","uid":109923,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"869359719e7451f85bbe2877dcc1e106611370d9","tid":2026805,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:44:45.000Z","msg":"PlayStation 中國商店無限期暫停服務後，近日 Microsoft Xbox One 中國版也封鎖了其他地區的商店，玩家沒法再透過破解漏洞到其他商店購買遊戲。<br />\n <br />\nXbox 上周五（15日）為「優化」系統性能，全球更新至 2493 系統。然而，有 Xbox One 中國版玩家在更新後，發現商店地區自動改成「中國區」，也無法再破解切換到其他區域的商店購買遊戲。Xbox One 中國版原設定只能使用中國國內的遊戲，但只要插進載有指定文件的 USB 儲存裝置進行破解，玩家便能夠切換到香港、美國等地的商店購買遊戲，連中國沒通過審批的遊戲也可以玩。<br />\n<br />\n中國網民也擔心繼 PlayStation 和 Xbox 後，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Nintendo Switch 和 Steam</span></strong> 也會封鎖，那麼中國玩家以後便只能玩中國共產黨容許的遊戲了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FiDSGET.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFiDSGET.jpg&h=8e95482e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料來源：4Gamers"},{"pid":"ad1a1fec4abbfa0f2a64086cc613b17f7f7777e6","tid":2026805,"uid":46323,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:45:40.000Z","msg":"Switch唔係鎖咗喇咩，黃之鋒動森丫嘛<br />\n<br />\n淨返Steam<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0a4aeceaf34d6a9bf74b749b22d08e7de6f1c5","tid":2026805,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:47:51.000Z","msg":"唔明, 玩水貨實體版唔得咩?"},{"pid":"bc31e0c09266e90ddf1bc606085446f221eb77d4","tid":2026805,"uid":33730,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ad1a1fec4abbfa0f2a64086cc613b17f7f7777e6","tid":2026805,"uid":46323,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:45:40.000Z","msg":"Switch唔係鎖咗喇咩，黃之鋒動森丫嘛<br />\n<br />\n淨返Steam<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited